{"tid":2124170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴士減班次即係啲人又坐返密啲","createTime":"2020-07-25T08:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T01:12:06.000Z","uid":26084,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f160cac1203249efab7cead853530ec7dff2aa4","tid":2124170,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【星島日報報道】受新冠肺炎第三波疫情影響，巴士公司的乘客量大減，九巴、城巴、新巴及龍運巴士就營運情況於較早前向運輸署申請暫時調整部分巴士路線。 受交通服務需求減少影響，九巴宣布經已獲運輸署批准調整部份巴士路線。76條巴士路線將於7月27日 (星期一) 起進行臨時班次調整，為期一星期。31P、271S、N41X路線服務將會暫停直至另行通告。另外，五條路線1、2F、3C、5及11，在上周調整班次後，將於同日恢復正常班次。<br />\n<br />\n九巴受影響的路線，其日間繁忙時間及非繁忙時間，乘客等候時間不會延長超過5分鐘。至於晚間9時後的非繁忙時間，等候時間不會延長超過10分鐘。調整後，所有路線每班車等候時間不會超過30分鐘。九巴會繼續密切留意實際營運情況及客量，適時作出車務調配以應付乘客需求變化。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁點撚樣對抗疫情呀？</strong>"},{"pid":"bbfcdeee69e8206d7574b09fa17dea7be8b62b02","tid":2124170,"uid":315798,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V88kCsL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV88kCsL.png&h=09d1c738&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a396abe3eb81f1ed1f23cd9875e3703a4d097341","tid":2124170,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbfcdeee69e8206d7574b09fa17dea7be8b62b02","tid":2124170,"uid":315798,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V88kCsL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV88kCsL.png&h=09d1c738&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5A72tyX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5A72tyX.jpg&h=2f064366&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e2c79b5aaf54d1d663313332c82cf78fdd38e7f","tid":2124170,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a396abe3eb81f1ed1f23cd9875e3703a4d097341","tid":2124170,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid